{"tid":449644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★黃之鋒出獄 唔適應手機筷子背囊","createTime":"2017-10-27T11:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T05:33:30.000Z","uid":19454,"like":16,"dislike":81,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"f525dcfd28cead3ca5742d9758f1134eb003aa42","tid":449644,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:04:55.000Z","msg":"法庭日前批准香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒保釋等候上訴後，黃之鋒尋日喺Facebook貼文講出獄感受，指自己對手機、筷子同背囊都唔適應，仲話<span style=\"color: red;\">出獄後嘅節奏唔可以好似入獄前咁急促，亦喺獄中領悟到有時步伐要緩慢啲。</span><br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒喺貼文中話當日下午四點恢復人身自由嗰一刻，就開始發現自己不太對勁。佢話手握嗰部「久別重逢」嘅電話，開機嗰刻係有種莫名其妙嘅陌生感，居然諗：「點解呢舊嘢會發光嘅？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">希望恢復正常生活</span><br />\n<br />\n佢承認出獄後嘅節奏唔可以好似入獄前咁急促，而喺在囚好一段日子後，真係需要時間適應。佢仲話喺獄中領悟到有時步伐要緩慢啲，畀自己有多啲時間沉澱，佢又希望呢幾日調整身心，恢復一般人嘅正常生活。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20171027/00176_131.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171027%2F00176_131.html&d=ueduJ9UI%2FfU5gbN3igvYfp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=f5d14775\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20171027/00176_131.html</a>"},{"pid":"2bb756062ab70fd1f843b7058c41c78f3df65fef","tid":449644,"uid":19454,"like":210,"dislike":2,"score":208,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:06:12.000Z","msg":"監獄生活仲好過獄外香港？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687fb8f65eb5b45b99835cf9f86731e4287c964f","tid":449644,"uid":36035,"like":19,"dislike":170,"score":-151,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:08:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25a7e1b802f6203c89e69a3c919af4407425840a","tid":449644,"uid":7699,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:10:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔適應手機、筷子、背囊<br />\n<br />\n適唔適應錢詩文個西？駛唔駛我代勞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肥到成隻豬咁都啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gi